      "content": "\u003cdiv class\u003d\"introduction img-head\"\u003e\r\n  \u003cdiv class\u003d\"header\"\u003e\r\n        \u003cimg src\u003d\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,\u003d\u003d\" alt\u003d\"App Icon\"\u003e\r\n    \u003ch3\u003eInventory Safety Stock Optimization Analytical App\u003c/h3\u003e\r\n  \u003c/div\u003e\r\n\r\n  \u003csection\u003e\r\n    \u003ch4\u003eOverview\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n    \u003cp\u003eThis App is designed to help businesses, like Lumax, align inventory levels with demand forecasts to minimize excess stock while maintaining high service levels. By using advanced statistical methods, the app ensures optimized material availability, reduces working capital blockage, and brings transparency to inventory decisions.\u003c/p\u003e\r\n  \u003c/section\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003csection\u003e\r\n    \u003ch4\u003eInput\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n    \u003cul\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003eThe app ingests material master and transaction-level data directly from source systems.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003eKey input attributes include SKU identifiers, material descriptions, unit price, unit of measure, historical weekly demand, demand variability (standard deviation), peak demand, supplier lead times, and lot sizes.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003eThese inputs are used to compute average weekly demand and apply multiple safety stock methods (Statistical, Max-Average, Time-Coverage) for comparative analysis.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n       \u003c/ul\u003e\r\n  \u003c/section\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003csection\u003e\r\n    \u003ch4\u003eOutput\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n    \u003cul\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003eThe app provides optimized safety stock recommendations for each SKU using statistical models, along with cost impact comparisons across methods like Statistical, Max-Average, and Time-Coverage.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003eService Level Assurance — Maintains 95–99% SLA across SKUs.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003eSKU-wise Safety Stock Reduction insights (15–51% reduction).\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003eProvides optimized safety stock recommendations with cost comparisons and includes EDA-driven insights on demand, lead time, and inventory trends to support strategic inventory decisions.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n       \u003c/ul\u003e\r\n  \u003c/section\u003e\r\n\r\n  \u003csection\u003e\r\n    \u003ch4\u003eBenefits\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n    \u003cul\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003eVisual diagnostics through EDA to validate demand consistency, supply reliability, and inventory drivers.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003eReduce excess inventory to release working capital.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003eImprove material availability for planned sales.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003eValidate and adjust MRP parameters scientifically.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003eStrategic Inventory Planning: Helps prioritize overstock consumption and tailor approaches for seasonal/promotional SKUs.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n     \r\n      \u003c/ul\u003e\r\n  \u003c/section\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n",
